Building-wiring safety-net + ground-truth debug; VIP via purchase (no auto-grant)

Chasing the recurring "buildings show no price / can't upgrade" regression:

- StadiumController: added a standalone retry loop (1s x30) that re-attempts wiring
  any unwired building independent of profile pushes, so a replication race can't
  leave one permanently dead. Exposes wiredCount() for diagnostics.
- ClientMain debug overlay now shows GROUND TRUTH: which controllers loaded
  (S/U/P/B/K/H +/-), stadium wired=N/tagged=M, and captures StadiumController
  onProfileUpdated errors into the readout.

VIP (as requested — buy it yourself, no auto-grant):
- Removed the Studio auto-VIP grant.
- MonetizationService: PromptGamePassPurchaseFinished now grants a pass the instant
  its purchase completes (Studio test purchases included) + pushes profile, so
  buying VIP works live without rejoining.

